![Episode19.jpg](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1575129069589-XX71N5OFCWAFUTBX5HJ9/Episode19.jpg)

It is time once again to dive into the DARKNESS as the guys at Major Issues finish thier recap and review of the DC Crossover Event Dark Nights Metal. In an episode so BIG it had to be split into two parts, the guys discuss the Nightmare Batmen, Godzilla in Hawkman form, Dr Fate who's MIA, and how does one ride a dragon?  
  
If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the one stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
